{"tid":1555752,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"9 月啦, 仲有人唔鎖電話? 你自己死算啦, 唔好害死成班手足同律師團啦屌你老母","createTime":"2019-09-09T12:53:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T15:35:10.000Z","uid":51701,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9659a9b3670e267dbaabbeaa2cb5eced6ed0fc6d","tid":1555752,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:53:25.000Z","msg":"有律師講到直到尋日為止仍然發生緊嘅問題：<br />\n<br />\n（一）電話唔落密碼（聽聞原因係唔想女朋友唔信自己）(ps. 指紋都唔應該)<br />\n（二）畀差佬嚇兩嚇落晒口供<br />\n（三）衰多口（得一句你可以講：我冇嘢講）<br />\n<br />\n依家得唔到400位義務律師去做，本身已經要兼顧工作同義救已經攰，面對喱啲無奈嘅事係更攰，拍硬檔了解自己應該做啲咩。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以上三點我屌晒你地老母, <br />\n害到律師團死死下,<br />\n又係口供上/電話上無意中篤灰,<br />\n<br />\n最後想講一句<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">屌晒你地老母</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"73ad845b993565e4c60e72ca141e40eae5249b95","tid":1555752,"uid":258370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:53:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"556d7a9a3a7372fb6ce09ef428d3e31dc22ef7d3","tid":1555752,"uid":55375,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:54:13.000Z","msg":"冇覺悟會俾人兇就咪撚出"},{"pid":"7684d44eb2a8fe8d3aaaba002e11f6c43f6b85dc","tid":1555752,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"556d7a9a3a7372fb6ce09ef428d3e31dc22ef7d3","tid":1555752,"uid":55375,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:54:13.000Z","msg":"冇覺悟會俾人兇就咪撚出"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T13:52:01.000Z","msg":"唔小心比人引導就篤左身邊有幾多人出黎<br />\n警犬一定間瘋狂砌案件拼圖"},{"pid":"440c3993e8bc40b265b4deecebfbf0c8b150be3e","tid":1555752,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T13:54:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7b2f39fe463e5a05718a2ced686340a5999f14fd","tid":1555752,"uid":16846,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T13:54:37.000Z","msg":"驚女朋友擔心咪講個密碼佢知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />